  "text": "LOH analysis was performed exactly as described elsewhere [CITATION_1] using fluorescent primers tagged with HEX or FAM for microsatellite markers on chromosome 1p36 (D1S468, D1S1612, D1S228 and D1S214) and chromosome 19q13 (D19S219, D19S412 and D19-HRC). PCR products were analysed by capillary electrophoresis. Diagnostic criteria for LOH required the calculated ratio of the peak areas to be less than 0.5.",
